This paper is primarily focused on data exchange, which is a subfield of databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the semantics of mappings between schemas, which is related to logic (cs.LO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The dichotomy results mentioned in the paper are related to computational complexity (cs.DS) and complexity theory (cs.CC).
